    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd0">-You killed all the rulers. I.. I thank you so much for saving our world.. But..</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd1">-You have a dark soul within you.. which you inherited from the Pygmy.. And it also needs to be returned to the great flame..</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd2">*The Undying let out a heavy sigh*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd3">-Don't be afraid.. The great flame will consume you.. And you will gain peace, Lost Soul.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd4">*The Undying turned to ponder everything*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd5">-Please.. Don't be afraid.. I will help you..*Approaching The Undying from behind and hugging him*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd6">*The Undying turned to the flame keeper, then nodded to her*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd7">-Thank you.. Farewell..</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd8">*Touching The Undying. She released his soul*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd9">*The process was not pleasant*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyGoodEnd10">*After the flame keeper returned all the souls to the great flame.. The balance was restored to the world..*</system:String>


    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd0">-I see that you have been consumed by darkness..</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd1">-Why did you do this.. Now our world will perish.. And the great flame will go out.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd2">*The Undying says* -Now I am the ruler of this world.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd3">*Emilia* -I won't let you..</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd4">*The Undying drew his sword, then swung it and killed Emilia with a quick strike*</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd5">-Now the great flame is within me.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd6">-Now I am the king of this world.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyDarkEnd7">-And no one will stand in my way..</system:String>

    <system:String x:Key="storyOfTheDeceased0">After Undying's death, the world began to be consumed by darkness.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyOfTheDeceased1">The world plunged into darkness and chaos, and people could not find a way to restore balance.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyOfTheDeceased2">However, not all hope was lost.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="storyOfTheDeceased3">There was a legend that there are still the Unextinguished ones in the world who will restore balance to the world.</system:String>

